discussion_comments.comment_body:
@madolson From the POV of OSS users, these are critical interfaces to manage and deploy a Redis Cluster. 
IMHO we need to show how to operate a Redis cluster. If someone wants to implement a different TD or FC, it's up to them. 
What we should do is (per command) mark it either (1) Admin interface or (2) Cluster Control interface. which can indicate if you must implement it (2) or not (1).
